<h1>Portfolio</h1>
<h2>A1</h2>
<p>For this assignment, I chose to do poem 4. This one was most diffuclt for me to do but I tried to take the overall theme of the poem and express it musically. I have it set up as 3 distinct parts. Part 2 and part 3 are signaled by an erupt guitar chord that symbalizes the sudden struck mentioned within the poem. Part 2 has to do with looking into past experiences, so I tried using the choir to express an ambient atmosphere. In part 3, I tried to express the moving forward tone of the poem with quick guitar transitions</p>
