<h2>A3</h2>
<p>For this assignment, I tried to stick to the brief as much as I could. For the first part of the video, I have a moderate guitar pace being played along with some machine noises and a subtle beat in the back. The second part, I have a beat being played in the backround as well as siren noises going off. In the third part, I sped up the guitar melody and raised the volume of the beat to enrich the texture</P>
